WEBVTT

00:00.478 --> 00:01.950
Hi! I'm Leo.

00:02.906 --> 00:04.243
Dancing is my hobby.

00:05.275 --> 00:08.231
In my free time, I travel with my friends.

00:08.840 --> 00:10.659
I also enjoy going to the beach.

00:11.326 --> 00:15.091
When I'm not busy, I like to read and write poems.

00:16.187 --> 00:18.947
I also think drawing is fun and enjoyable.

00:19.754 --> 00:22.377
When I want to relax, I watch TV...

00:22.942 --> 00:24.160
...or go running outside.

00:24.806 --> 00:25.555
What about you?

00:26.078 --> 00:27.305
What are your hobbies?

